summary: Third version of Jenassa Half-elf I have done but this time gave her some Altmer (High-elf) features and Redguard skin. Choose UNP or CBBEV3!
descriptionHtml:
Updated 04/20/12 unibody, changed stance to female and minor face tweaks around lips and cheeks. 

***If you are updating from the previous version you will need to remove file #000b9982 from Facegoem Meshes and Face Tint Texture folders or she will not display properly!***

Jenassa Half-elf Altmer-Redguard Follower

Third version of Jenassa but this time gave her Altemr (High-elf) features. Father High-elf Justicar, mother Redguard Housecarl. Nature took its course or he had his way, it\'s unknown. Jenassa was born and became a sell-sword later in life. 

Used Jenassa\'s voice with this version. 

Inventory: No clothes! I will leave that to your imagination. 
Weapon: Two Redguard Scimitar\'s

Age: Unknown (mid-years)
Voice: Jenassa\'s
Body: *dimon99\'s UNP Dimonized Body or CBBEV3 Curvy with *Navetsea\'s Skin, Muscle and Thin Landing Strip, *Glosstech No Shine v05. 
Hair: Apachii #24 hair. 
Thin and tall, Weight 55 (approximately 165 lbs) and High-elf Height .97 (approximately 6.1 feet tall)
Face: *Bella Female Faces: Full with No Shine
Eyes: *RANs Eyeliner Replacer by RAN46

See Images for stats, spells, perks and general character info please. 

If there is an (*) Asterisk by the named items above you will \"need\" these files to make her look similar to this version of Jenassa. 

*One Important Note* To get the hands to match in Navetsea\'s mod you need to copy the meshes from the Dimonized UNP MAIN folder to your Data Meshes Folder then overwrite with Navetsea\'s file. If you think this is a pain in the ass, just use the Dimon mod without Navetsea\'s mod. If you want a better looking body, female nether region and like your ladies fit, Navetsea has an excellent mod and is recommended! 


*If you are having an issue getting her to look right try this below.* 

\"For those who already have a modded Jenassa in their game. Load this mod, then go to Jenassa in game and use the console to \"setnpcweight 45\" on her, get out of the console, create a new save, exit the game entirely, then load the new save when you start the game again.\"

Thanks for checking her out!

FalmerBane
